<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.8">
<l>vāḷoṇ kaṇṇallār tāṅkaḷma taṉaṉeṉ ṟārtammai</l>
<l>kēḷmiṉī  ḷaiyō ṭēṅkuki ḻavaṉeṉ ṉātamuṉ</l>
<l>vēḷvum viḻavum vītiyi leṉṟuma ṟātavūr</l>
<l>nāḷu naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tummeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before women with cruel, bright eyes can say, “Listen to the old man</l>
<l>Who is croaking with phlegm at us that [he is] Cupid,”</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship daily in Naṟaiyūr,</l>
<l>The city where rituals and festivals forever in the streets never end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
